label: Very Low
comment: Likely to fail or otherwise cause problems within minutes.

label: Low
comment: Likely to fail or otherwise cause problems within hours to days.

label: Medium
comment: Likely to fail or otherwise cause problems every year or so.

label: High
comment: May fail or otherwise cause problems within the lifetime of a typical system.

label: Very High
comment: Unlikely to fail or otherwise cause problems within the lifetime of a typical system.

label: Safe
comment: Will never fail or otherwise cause problems.
